org.lobobrowser.http

Interface UserAgentContext

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    UserAgentContextImpl

    public interface UserAgentContext
    Provides information about the user agent (browser) driving the parser and/or renderer.

    A simple implementation of this interface is provided in org.lobobrowser.html.test.SimpleUserAgentContext.

    See Also:
    HtmlRendererContext#getUserAgentContext(), DocumentBuilderImpl.DocumentBuilderImpl(UserAgentContext)
